OL,3,CPolice pursuit before stolen car
OL,4,Ccrashed into care home 'exemplary' `
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FPolice officers pursued the car for
OL,8,Ffour minutes, treating the case as a
OL,9,Fpossible kidnapping as the offenders
OL,10,Fhad driven off with an unrelated
OL,11,Fmember of the public.
OL,13,FTwo elderly care home residents
OL,14,Fsuffered broken bones and the building
OL,15,Fwas evacuated due to structural damage
OL,16,Fand a collapsed ceiling.
