OL,4,Ccrashed into care home 'exemplary' `
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,8,FConduct (IOPC) carried out an inquiry
OL,9,Finto the pursuit and found that the
OL,10,Fofficers had behaved in an "exemplary"
OL,11,Fmanner.
OL,13,FThey said although the officer's speed
OL,14,Fexceeded 90mph, their actions were
OL,15,F"justified" and the police driver kept
OL,16,Fa safe distance from the BMW.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
