OL,3,CPolice pursuit before stolen car
OL,4,Ccrashed into care home 'exemplary' `
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FThe IOPC director Emily Barry said:
OL,8,F"This must have been a terrifying
OL,9,Fincident, particularly for the care
OL,10,Fhome residents and staff, and my
OL,11,Fthoughts are with all those affected.
OL,13,F"Our independent investigation has
OL,14,Fmade clear that the responsibility for
OL,15,Fthis collision, and the resulting
OL,16,Finjuries, lies solely with the BMW
OL,17,Fdriver, who had every opportunity to
OL,18,Fdo the right thing and stop for police
OL,19,F- but chose instead to put lives at
OL,20,Frisk.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
