OL,3,CPolice pursuit before stolen car
OL,4,Ccrashed into care home 'exemplary' `
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,F"This was a thorough investigation,
OL,8,Fand I am grateful that all officers
OL,9,Finvolved co-operated fully with our
OL,10,Finquiries, which helped us conclude
OL,11,Four work swiftly.
OL,13,F"The evidence shows that, despite
OL,14,Fbeing faced with an extremely
OL,15,Fchallenging situation, all officers
OL,16,Finvolved acted in an exemplary manner."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
