OL,7,FThe driver, Sam Asgari-Tabar, 21, was
OL,8,Fjailed for five years and two months
OL,9,Fat Newcastle Crown Court in November
OL,10,Fafter pleading guilty to robbery and
OL,11,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,12,Fdriving.
OL,14,FReece Parish, 21, of Fordham Road,
OL,15,FSunderland, was jailed for 19 months
OL,16,Fafter pleading guilty to robbery.
